    "The toolkit validates and outputs the Model Card as a structured JSON file.",
    "The actual model file (for example, a PyTorch.pt file) is uploaded to an artifact store such as HuggingFace or GitHub.",
    "The model card entry is updated with a link to the artifact's location.",
    "At this point, the model becomes available in the system's model catalog.Runtime Data Capture.",
    "The zig-zag arrows pointing inward in Figure 2 are runtime information collection points."
